column5: Was looking to book a trip to snow lake in manitoba. Wanted some feedback on the walleye fishing, size of the lake and accomodations. Thanks for the help.

Are you thinking about fishing Snow lake or lakes in the area? I can hook you up with some info on that area as I fish this area.And know a lodge owner on a body of water that produces big Walleye's in the Snow lake area. Throw me an email. NMhttp://www.xtremesportfishing.com/forum
